I have to thank this blog(https://livestorm.co/blog/marketing-webinar-automation-one-click-registrations-from-email-campaigns) for kicking off this great idea of a) showing me another way to a) create a user subscription without transfering the user off your webite and b) creating a very elegant solution to the challenge. 

This tutorial will cover integration between a website hosted on Firebase.com, a Mailchimp newletter, a Zapier zap and a Kandy.io SMS notification. 
